product.name: L'Oreal Extraordinaire Gel Lacque Nail Colour
product.description: L’Oréal Paris introduces the Extraordinaire Gel-Lacque 1-2-3 system for perfectly shaped, volumized nails and rich, ultra-glossy colour.This is a three-step nail system: GEL-PRIMER - Apply 1 coat of gel primer to build volume and prepare nails for optimized colour pay-off.GEL-COLOUR - Apply 2 coats of gel colour. Achieve rich, glossy colour and plumped-up nails.GEL-GLAZE - Apply 1 coat of gel glaze. Achieve incredible shine.
